title: Detect existing post-commit hook
status: OPEN
date: 2008-09-18 00:48:51+0300
author: Ilmari Heikkinen <ilmari.heikkinen@gmail.com>

-- opened by Ilmari Heikkinen <ilmari.heikkinen@gmail.com> on 2008-09-18 00:48:51+0300

Problem description:
 gitbug init or gitbug use_autoclose 
 can screw up an existing post-commit hook

Proposed solution:
 Check whether there exists a post-commit hook,
 tell user to add the autoclose to the hook manually.
